Mac App Store: &lt;a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/domprompter-ai-coding-prompt/id6761685716?mt=12"&gt;https://apps.apple.com/us/app/domprompter-ai-coding-prompt/i...&lt;/a&gt;&lt;p&gt;Would love feedback from people doing front-end / vibe-coding style workflows.&lt;/p&gt;
